<%#
  CategoryLearningSuggestionRow — 인라인 카테고리 변경 후 행 바로 아래에
  렌더되는 "학습 제안" 행 (ADR-0007 §4).

  방금 변경한 거래의 merchant + category로 explicit opt-in 학습을 제안한다.
  수락 시 CategoryLearningSuggestionsController#create로 POST, CategoryMapping
  생성 후 turbo_stream로 본 행을 제거. 거절 시 클라이언트가 본 행을 DOM에서
  제거(서버 호출 없음).

  Locals:
    transaction (Transaction, required) — 방금 카테고리가 변경된 거래

  Workspaces/transactions 테이블 컬럼 수(6)와 colspan 일치 필요.
%>
<tr id="category-learning-suggestion-<%= transaction.id %>"
    data-controller="category-learning-suggestion"
    data-category-learning-suggestion-url-value="<%= workspace_transaction_category_learning_suggestion_path(@workspace, transaction) %>"
    data-category-learning-suggestion-category-id-value="<%= transaction.category_id %>"
    data-category-learning-suggestion-merchant-value="<%= transaction.merchant.to_s.strip %>"
    class="bg-ai-subtle">
  <td colspan="6" class="px-4 py-3">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <p class="text-meta text-primary"><%= t("transactions.category_learning_suggestion.body") %></p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 shrink-0">
        <button type="button"
                data-action="click->category-learning-suggestion#accept"
                class="px-3 py-1 text-meta font-medium rounded-md bg-action text-action-on hover:bg-action-hover">
          <%= t("transactions.category_learning_suggestion.accept") %>
        </button>
        <button type="button"
                data-action="click->category-learning-suggestion#dismiss"
                class="px-3 py-1 text-meta text-secondary hover:bg-elev rounded-md">
          <%= t("transactions.category_learning_suggestion.dismiss") %>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </td>
</tr>
